title: Print, "Female Head With Pendant: 1935 in Reverse", 1935
description: An ovoid face is framed by shoulder-length wavy hair. Facial features include closed eyes, depicted by thinly drawn curves embellished by eyelashes comprised of short strokes; a long, straight nose; and full closed lips. A pendant, suspended from a loop-and-ball patterned necklace, is comprised of the numerals 7, 3, 9, and 1, representing the year 1935, in reverse.
